data.description: Located in the coveted Glenkirk Estates neighborhood, this remarkable single-family home epitomizes luxury living!    As you step through the grand entrance, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light, hardwood floors, and an open floor plan that is perfect for both family living and entertaining guests. The spacious living area boasts high ceilings, elegant finishes, and a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.  The main level is spacious and well appointed, with multiple dining areas, a luxurious family room, a gourmet kitchen, a sunroom, and lots of space for storage in the mud room off the garage!  The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a large center island, and ample cabinet space. Whether you're hosting a formal dinner party or enjoying a casual meal with family, this kitchen is sure to impress!  Retreat to the luxurious master suite, where you'll find a peaceful oasis complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom and a spacious walk-in closets. Additional bedrooms offer plenty of room for guests or family members, each appointed with plush carpeting and generous closet space.  Step outside to your own private sanctuary, where lush landscaping and a beautifully manicured lawn create the perfect backdrop for outdoor relaxation and entertainment. Enjoy al fresco dining on the deck or gather around the patio fire pit on cooler evenings.  The location is amazing, offering convenient access to top-rated schools, shopping, dining, local wineries and breweries, and plenty of recreational amenities.
